g.title: Legend
g.text: 2 - Generate ID, init timestamps, verify signature, set status to 'init'
3 - Write action into database and scheduler spool
5 - Find target agents, set status 'preparing', write to database
6 - Generate one command per action into the scheduler spool
7 - Process new commands from the scheduler spool
8 - Write command to database, set status to 'sent'
10 - Update action in database, set status to 'inflight'
11 - Push commands from relay to agents
12 - Return commands results from agents to relay
13 - Push returned commands from relay to scheduler
14 - Process returned commands from scheduler spool
15 - Write results to database, set command status to 'success'
16 - Notify action updater that command has finished
17 - When all commands are done, set action status to 'done'
